Joel Steiger (born March 11, 1942) is an American television producer, writer, and director. He specializes in creating mystery series. Has worked as writer, executive producer and consultant on some of the most successful television mysteries of the 80's & 90's. Steiger has won one Edgar Award in 1983 for "Remington Steele" for episode "In the Steele Of The Night".
